Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate won't close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is the gate closed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on now?\NI want a status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-The Extinction Belt has descended so low.\N-Show me the footage of camera 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anomaly detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no sign of it receding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your ETA?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll arrive in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and causing all sorts of malfunctions\Nto the defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the Extinction Belt\Nis still descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The activity of Kunad Gate along\Nwith gravitational anomaly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Extinction Belt continues to descend...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to happen again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yuito holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes he seems to be in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ready the ward for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But given the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there is any hospital\Nthat is available.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create\Na relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone\Nsomewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here\Nand between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now,\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’ll see I’m always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller coaster\Ninside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and\Nthe unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,INTO THE CRYPT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi, I know you are worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's too risky to teleport with Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's never going to wake up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He threw a lot of arrogant words at me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he can prove his ideal is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he's not going to die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I can say about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,your authority as Chief has been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon arriving Suoh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,please continue to command the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an expandable pawn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,must be utilized to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the correct political decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Error on the defense system!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No confirmed downtime yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Arahabaki is the foundation for all,\Nstart repairing it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gates of certain shelters can't be closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,OSF soldiers are doing their best\Nto stop the Others' advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's only a matter of time before\Nthey break through our defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We are fighting an uphill battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our formation has been scattered,\Nwe can't coordinate in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon the inoperational defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Order all the soldiers deployed\Nnear the inoperable AA guns
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to evacuate to shelters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All stranded troops must\Nreturn to headquarters at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran is not doing any better\Nthan us in this chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not hope for any reinforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll clear a path to New Himuka's future\Nwith our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking over the command\Nwhile I was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot them! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The area of the eastern shelters\Nhas been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After you get everything under control,\Nmove on to the next shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a hospital in Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember hearing the Other alarm\Non the street of Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of Others on\Nthe street has been reduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The incidence rate has\Ngone down significantly as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't let the civilians\Nleave their shelters just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The defense system hasn't been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure if the Others will attack\Nthe streets again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We are awaiting orders from the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, we are preparing for the next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we need to head to the crypt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel much better after the long sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find Yakumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we need to find Karen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and undo the dimensional entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We must settle this once and for all\Nbefore it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just woke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll see how it goes for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sumeragi crypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Yuito really going to be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard what he said.\NWe can only take his words for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be worried about ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If my brother is inside the Sumeragi crypt,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to persuade him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight might be inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed. We must be ready for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the world is full of\Ndirty secrets and nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but no matter how twisted it's become,\Nending it is not the right solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens from now on,\NI won't abandon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the information about a dumpling shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to try it for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumpling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems like a place for youngsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have trouble fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly young anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count me in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too! Count me in as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious over here!\NAre you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The world will be safe with you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we should start making plans\Nfor our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind having dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, are you joining them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are countless lives here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want them to perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you wouldn't want that either, Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist on fighting Karen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be able to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not relying on you to protect me, Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly be so full of myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe everyone and I will\Nstill be able to crack some jokes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, you should believe that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too harsh, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm totally serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, you never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many things I'd like to comment on,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but can you at least don't eat in my room\Nwhile lying on the couch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me, I won't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have work tomorrow morning.\NIt's almost bedtime for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to bed if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember raising you to be so stern.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember you ever raising me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave the streets to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the monsters to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you have that troublesome friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky I came to visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still too weak to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But your brain power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, Naomi, Captain Seto,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget how they lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how long it takes,\NI will never overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is built upon\Nsacrifices and tragedies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are using brain power to heal the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but we pursue stronger power\Nwhile we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Many have fallen into the abyss of madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We must put an end to all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This world can't rely solely on\Nbrain power to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People who control brain power
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,will unknowingly become controlled\Nby their own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we can live in a world where no one\Nneeds to rely on power to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we must destroy the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought you were\Njust another unreliable brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you can change\Nthe world for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.\NI'll finally be able to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane, can you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to gather up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move out in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even I can find any data
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,about the Sumeragi crypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a totally unknown realm in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the OSF headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How did we suddenly get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have fallen into some kind of\Nteleportation trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the surrounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is without a doubt very creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it might have something\Nto do with my brother's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Other alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A large number of Others are raining down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter retaliation formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Other incidence rate has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That might just be an illusion of Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister was here before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are sitting ducks in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it won't be easy to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma, above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We are experiencing my brother's pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we can all be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the emotions will consume us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we can all be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we can all be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I fail again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, live on for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stay here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose my consciousness just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumeragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,THE YEARNING IN SLUMBER
